            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/36113691/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/36113691/" class="">第103页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/la07/" class=" " title="悦怿">悦怿</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="36113691">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">人类的历史从此是一个多少盲目地为认可一个共同目的而努力的历史……
</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2015-09-14 11:56</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>人类的历史从此是一个多少盲目地为认可一个共同目的而努力的历史……</q></blockquote>

                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
